name: I was made by humans
description:
Re-born and re-forged in the clutches
of mankind, its existence iterating
over and over in pollution, noise, and
plastic that won't degrade. Cursed
with an infinite lifespan from its
patchwork skin of loud colors and
patterns, it rages across the
landscape as a hollow form of its
original self. It only becomes even
more lost as time passes, with more
shells and layers forming to further
obscure its exterior and core.
